<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: After finishing her student years, [PAWN_nameDef] successfully passed the military entrance exam and voluntarily enlisted as a soldier in the Wolfein MegaCorp. [PAWN_nameDef] always maintained a positive attitude, full of creativity, and excelled at finding innovative solutions to problems in high-pressure environments. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_01.description>[PAWN_nameDef]在学生时代结束后顺利通过了参军考核，自愿加入了沃芬军企，成为一名士兵。[PAWN_nameDef]始终保持积极的态度，富有创造力，擅长在紧张的环境中找到解决问题的创新方式。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_01.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp recruit -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_01.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队新兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_01.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp recruit -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_01.titleShort>军企新兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_01.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: Upon learning that it was the ResistanceArmy who carried out the terrorist attack in the city, [PAWN_nameDef] was filled with intense rage. With her passionate nature, she enlisted without hesitation and became a soldier in the MegaCorp, secretly vowing to drive these rebels out of their homeland -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_02.description>在得知是抵抗军在城市内实施恐怖袭击后，[PAWN_nameDef]感到异常愤怒。满腔热血的[PAWN_nameDef]毫不犹豫地参军，成为了军企的士兵，并暗自发誓，一定要将这些叛军驱逐出他们的家园。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_02.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp recruit -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_02.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队新兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_02.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp recruit -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_02.titleShort>军企新兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_02.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: Feeling lost about her future, [PAWN_nameDef] enlisted in the military on the recommendation of others. Living alongside fellow recruits helped her gradually find clarity in her path forward. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_03.description>[PAWN_nameDef]对未来感到迷茫，在他人的推荐下，[PAWN_nameDef]选择了参军。与其他新兵一起生活的日子让她的人生道路逐渐变得清晰起来。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_03.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp recruit -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_03.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队新兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_03.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp recruit -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_03.titleShort>军企新兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_03.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of the Wolfein Task Force, assigned to the fringes to carry out security duties for the Wolfein colonies, defending against the ResistanceArmy. [PAWN_nameDef] hopes that, once the civil war ends, she will be able to return to her family and live a peaceful life. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_04.description>[PAWN_nameDef]隶属于沃芬特遣机动队，所在部队被派往边缘世界执行沃芬族殖民地的安保任务，以抵御抵抗军的威胁。[PAWN_nameDef]希望有朝一日内战结束后，能重新回到家人身边，过上平静的生活。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_04.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_04.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_04.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_04.titleShort>军企士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_04.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is part of the Wolfein Task Force, and the constant battles against the resistance have left her mentally and physically exhausted. [PAWN_nameDef] finds herself questioning the reason for her fight—why, as members of the same race, must they engage in such mutual destruction? -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_05.description>[PAWN_nameDef]隶属于沃芬特遣机动队，与抵抗军的频繁交战让她感到身心俱疲。[PAWN_nameDef]开始不禁思考自己战斗的意义，为什么身为同胞彼此却要互相残杀。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_05.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_05.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_05.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_05.titleShort>军企士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_05.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of the Wolfein Task Force, harboring deep hatred for the terrorist organization known as the resistance. With each successive terrorist attack in the city, [PAWN_nameDef]'s resolve to oppose the resistance grows even stronger. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_06.description>[PAWN_nameDef]隶属于沃芬特遣机动队，深深痛恨这群自称为抵抗军的恐怖主义组织。随着城市内一次又一次恐怖袭击事件的发生，[PAWN_nameDef]与抵抗军为敌的决心愈加坚定。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_06.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_06.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_06.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_06.titleShort>军企士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_06.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of the Wolfein Task Force, and over time, she has lost the passion and ambition she once had. After countless battles, [PAWN_nameDef] has become numb, choosing to abandon further thought—she only needs to follow her superiors' orders without question. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_07.description>[PAWN_nameDef]隶属于沃芬特遣机动队，随着时间的推移，她逐渐失去了曾经的热血与抱负。在一次次战斗中变得麻木的[PAWN_nameDef]选择放弃思考，她只需要完全服从上级的命令，其他的都不再关心。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_07.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_07.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_07.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_07.titleShort>军企士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_07.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of the Wolfein Task Force, fully aware that the resistance was born to oppose the oppression of the lower classes by the Wolfein MegaCorp. However, when the actions of the resistance strayed from their original purpose, [PAWN_nameDef] realized that the resistance had become her enemy. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_08.description>[PAWN_nameDef]隶属于沃芬特遣机动队，深知抵抗军的诞生是为了反抗沃芬军工巨企对底层人民的压迫。然而，当抵抗军的行为与他们的初衷背道而驰时，[PAWN_nameDef]意识到，抵抗军已经成为了她的敌人。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_08.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_08.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_08.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_08.titleShort>军企士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_08.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of the Wolfein Task Force and has served in the military for many years. There are rumors that she once fought in the war against the Mechanoids and survived. Now, she is a seasoned veteran with extensive combat experience. Her journey has given her a profound understanding of organization and discipline, but it has also made her more cautious and vigilant, holding a reserved stance on how to resolve conflicts. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_09.description>[PAWN_nameDef]隶属于沃芬特遣机动队，已经在部队服役多年。传言称，她曾参与沃芬与机械族的战争，并成功幸存。如今，她已是个拥有丰富作战经验的老兵，[PAWN_nameDef]的经历让她对组织和纪律有着深刻的理解，但也使她变得更加警觉和慎重，对冲突的解决方式持保留态度。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_09.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_09.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_09.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_09.titleShort>军企士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_09.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of the Wolfein Task Force, and within the military, [PAWN_nameDef] operates like a cold, emotionless machine. No matter what task is assigned by the higher-ups, [PAWN_nameDef] accepts it without complaint. Whether it’s killing the enemy or being killed, [PAWN_nameDef] is mentally prepared for either outcome. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_10.description>[PAWN_nameDef]隶属于沃芬特遣机动队，在部队中，[PAWN_nameDef]就像一台冷血的机器，无论上级分派什么任务，[PAWN_nameDef]都毫无怨言地接受。杀敌或被杀，[PAWN_nameDef]早已做好了心理准备。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_10.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_10.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_10.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_10.titleShort>军企士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_10.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of the Wolfein Task Force, previously handling security-related matters. Amid the increasingly tense social environment, [PAWN_nameDef] was reassigned to the more dangerous and desolate Fringe Worlds, tasked with protecting the colonies of the Wolfein MegaCorp. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_11.description>[PAWN_nameDef]隶属于沃芬特遣机动队，曾负责安保事务。在社会环境日益紧张的背景下，[PAWN_nameDef]被调往更加危险且荒芜的边缘世界，承担起保护沃芬军工巨企殖民地的任务。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_11.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_11.title>沃芬族 军企特遣机动队士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_11.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp soldier -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_11.titleShort>军企士兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_11.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of a security detail within the Wolfein MegaCorp, responsible for escorting and transporting key personnel, critical cargo, and sensitive information. In the tense backdrop of the ongoing civil war, [PAWN_nameDef]'s duties have become all the more crucial. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_12.description>[PAWN_nameDef]隶属于沃芬军企的一支护卫队，护卫队日常负责重要人员、重要货物及信息的护送与运输。在紧张的内战局势下，[PAWN_nameDef]的护卫工作显得尤为重要。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_12.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp guard -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_12.title>沃芬族 军企护卫</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_12.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp guard -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_12.titleShort>军企护卫</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_12.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of the Wolfein MegaCorp's scout squad. As the vanguard of the unit, [PAWN_nameDef]'s duties include, but are not limited to, reconnaissance, sabotage, and gathering military intelligence. With her calm and decisive nature, as well as a keen awareness of environmental changes, [PAWN_nameDef] has become an excellent scout. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_13.description>[PAWN_nameDef]是沃芬军企斥候小队的一员，作为部队的先锋，[PAWN_nameDef]的任务不仅包括侦察、破坏与获取军事情报，还要求她保持高度的环境警觉性。凭借冷静果断的判断，[PAWN_nameDef]如今已经成长为一名出色的斥候。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_13.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp scout -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_13.title>沃芬族 军企斥候</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_13.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp scout -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_13.titleShort>军企斥候</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_13.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] serves as a military doctor within the Wolfein MegaCorp, having joined as a field medic with the intent of saving more lives on the frontlines. However, on the battlefield, [PAWN_nameDef] came to understand that in order to save one life, sometimes another must be ended. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_14.description>[PAWN_nameDef]在沃芬军企担任军医，成为随军医生的初衷是为了在前线救助更多的人。然而，在战场上，[PAWN_nameDef]逐渐领悟到，要拯救一条生命，有时必须先终结另一条生命。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_14.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp surgeon -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_14.title>沃芬族 军企医生</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_14.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp surgeon -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_14.titleShort>军企医生</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_14.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a sniper in a squad within the Wolfein MegaCorp, possessing extraordinary skills and a high level of professionalism. Even in extreme environments, [PAWN_nameDef] can maintain precise shooting. One bullet, one enemy—this is the result of [PAWN_nameDef]'s hard-earned training. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_15.description>[PAWN_nameDef]是沃芬军企中一支小队的狙击手，[PAWN_nameDef]有着超凡的技术与极高的专业素养，哪怕是在极端的环境里也可以保持精准的射击。一颗子弹，一名敌人，这正是[PAWN_nameDef]通过艰苦的训练得到的成果。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_15.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp sniper -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_15.title>沃芬族 军企狙击手</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_15.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp sniper -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_15.titleShort>军企狙击手</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_15.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] serves as a support soldier in a squad within the Wolfein MegaCorp. Wolfein support soldiers typically wear heavy armor and carry high-powered, sustained weapons to provide powerful fire support for their teammates. [PAWN_nameDef] is always the strongest pillar in the squad. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_16.description>[PAWN_nameDef]在沃芬军企的一支小队中担任支援兵。沃芬的支援兵通常穿戴重型护甲，携带高火力的持续武器，为队友提供强大的火力支援。[PAWN_nameDef]始终是小队中最坚强的后盾。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_16.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp support -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_16.title>沃芬族 军企支援兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_16.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp support -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_16.titleShort>军企支援兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_16.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a member of the Wolfein MegaCorp's Vanguard Squad. The members of the Vanguard are typically composed of melee units who have undergone specialized combat training. [PAWN_nameDef] was promoted to this elite squad due to her outstanding combat abilities and went on to achieve remarkable feats in several subsequent battles. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_17.description>[PAWN_nameDef]是沃芬军企尖兵小队的一员。尖兵队的成员通常由经过专业格斗训练的近战单位组成。[PAWN_nameDef]凭借出色的战斗能力被提拔进入这支精英小队，并在随后的多次战斗中立下赫赫战功。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_17.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp vanguard -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_17.title>沃芬族 军企尖兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_17.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp vanguard -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_17.titleShort>军企尖兵</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_17.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a combat mechanic in the Wolven military corporation. Due to the scarce population of the Wolven species, the actual number of Wolven soldiers in the military is significantly insufficient. As a result, the corporation makes extensive use of autonomous combat units within its military forces to compensate for this shortfall. After all, the cost of training a professional Wolven soldier far exceeds that of producing and maintaining autonomous machinery. Within the squad, [PAWN_nameDef]'s role is to command, calibrate, and maintain these autonomous combat machines. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_18.description>[PAWN_nameDef]是沃芬军企的一名战斗机械师。由于沃芬族人口稀少，军队中的实际沃芬数量远远不足。因此，军企在军工部队中大量使用自行机械战斗单位来弥补这一不足。毕竟，培养一名专业的沃芬士兵的成本远远高于制造和维护自行机械。在小队中，[PAWN_nameDef]的工作就是负责指挥、调试和维护这些自行战斗机械。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_18.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp mechanic -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_18.title>沃芬族 军企机械师</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_18.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp mechanic -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_18.titleShort>军企机械师</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_18.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has constantly tried to explain to those around her in the squad that she is not a hacker, but rather an "electronic warfare and intelligence acquisition specialist." Compared to other soldiers, [PAWN_nameDef] is not particularly skilled in combat, but her role in supporting combat is indispensable. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_19.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在小队中一直试图向周围的人解释，她并不是黑客，而是一位“电子战情报获取专家”。与其他成员相比，[PAWN_nameDef] 的战斗能力较弱，但她在辅助战斗中的作用却不可或缺。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_19.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp hacker -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_19.title>沃芬族 军企特战黑客</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_19.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp hacker -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_19.titleShort>军企特战黑客</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_19.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] holds a unique position within the Wolfein MegaCorp. Only a select few in the military are capable of using psychic powers in combat, and their role in battle is not to be underestimated. [PAWN_nameDef] was born with powerful psychic abilities and, upon reaching adulthood, was recruited into the MegaCorp as a psychic sorcerer. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_20.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在沃芬军企中的地位非常特殊。军队中只有极少数人能使用灵能进行作战，并且他们在战斗中的作用不可小觑。[PAWN_nameDef] 天生拥有强大的灵能，成年后，她以灵能术士的身份被招募进入了军企。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_20.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp psionic warlock -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_20.title>沃芬族 军企灵能术士</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_20.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp psionic warlock -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_20.titleShort>军企灵能术士</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_20.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] comes from a mysterious special forces squad within the MegaCorp, known as the "Red Hats." This elite squad is responsible for handling covert operations such as infiltration, assassination, intelligence theft, and sabotage. The distinctive red uniforms and hoods are the most obvious symbols of the "Red Hats." No one would dare to make an enemy of such a mysterious and formidable elite special forces unit. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_21.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 来自一支隶属于军企的神秘特种小队——“红帽”。这支特殊小队专门负责执行潜入、暗杀、情报窃取或设施破坏等秘密任务。统一的鲜红色制服与兜帽是“红帽”最显著的标识，没人愿意与这样一支神秘而可怕的精英特种小队为敌。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_21.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp "red-cap"team member -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_21.title>沃芬族 军企"红帽"特种队员</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_21.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp "red-cap"team member -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_21.titleShort>军企"红帽"特种队员</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_21.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a trade representative assigned to the frontlines by the MegaCorp’s trade department. She is responsible for negotiating material exchanges with local military forces and other colonies to secure the company's maximum profit. At the same time, [PAWN_nameDef] must also gather firsthand battlefield intelligence to support corporate decision-making. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_22.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 是沃芬军企商贸部门派驻前线的商贸代表。她负责与当地军事力量以及其他殖民地进行物资交易洽谈，以谋取公司最大利益。同时，[PAWN_nameDef] 还需要收集一手战场情报，为企业决策提供支持。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_22.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp Trader -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_22.title>沃芬族 军企商贸代表</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_22.title>
  <!-- EN: Mega Corp Trader -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_22.titleShort>军企商贸代表</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_22.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] successfully joined the administrative department of the MegaCorp through professional training and evaluation. As a civilian staff member responsible for administrative affairs, [PAWN_nameDef] handles various tedious paperwork and coordinates tasks between different departments. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_23.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 通过专业的培训考核，顺利加入了军工巨企的行政部门。作为一名负责行政事务的文职人员，[PAWN_nameDef] 需要处理各种繁琐的文书工作，并协调各部门之间的工作。</Wolfein_BackstoryMegaCorp_23.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp Clerk -->
